subSubSection.paragraph:
The male song has a wide band frequency spectrum with intensive components between 5–90 kHz (
Fig. 8
). Within that range three intensity peaks can be observed: a less intensive one between about 10-50 kHz and a more intensive range between about 19–30 kHz (peak frequence mean: 23.48 (min.-max. 15.73–28.92 ).

